"{\"uid\": \"rttnews.com-3463306-massive-attack-paralyzes-french-train-network-ahead-of-paris-olympics.aspx\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A few hours ahead of the Paris Olympics opening ceremony, France's high-speed rail lines were hit by a series of fires, disrupting travel nationwide.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998386949840136, \"rank\": 0.00012395876233261142, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French state rail company SNCF said it is a \\\"massive attack aimed at paralyzing the high-speed line network,\\\" and its Atlantic, Northern and Eastern high-speed lines were damaged in the arson attacks.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8373600495099273, \"rank\": 0.18006015716991677, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}, {\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Trains\", \"score\": 0.9970870740016248, \"rank\": 0.002725576801588595, \"text\": \"Northern\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Trains\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Trains\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A large number of trains were diverted or canceled,\\\" it wrote on X and urged \\\"all travelers who can to postpone their trip and not go to the station.\\\"\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thousands of customers will be affected with disruption expected through the weekend.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eurostar said a quarter of its services will be cancelled until Monday.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999984095211, \"rank\": 1.5904209447483273e-09, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The joint French-Swiss airport Basel-Mulhouse was evacuated and closed on Friday morning for safety reasons.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French transport minister condemned the \\\"co-ordinated malicious acts.\\\"\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8373600495099273, \"rank\": 0.18006015716991677, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the disruption, the inaugural ceremony of the Olympic Games will go on as scheduled on the Seine River.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Parade of Nations, thousands of athletes from participating nations will travel on boats through the heart of the city, waving to fans on the river bank.\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The number of attendees at the opening ceremony has been cut short due to security reasons.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the wake of the attacks, French Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin announced that security has been beefed up.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999108695, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\"}, {\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999985868856563, \"rank\": 1.33731647661934e-06, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"45,000-strong police force, 10,000 soldiers and 20,000 private security personnel have been deployed for the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris prosecutor's office said it has launched an investigation into the incidents that started overnight.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.200905345663184e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For comments and feedback contact: editorial@rttnews.com  Business News    November 28, 2025 15:30 ETSurvey data on the consumer confidence and housing demand attracted attention this week in the U.S. along with the weekly jobless claim figures.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Europe, the economic sentiment data from the euro area was in focus.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Further, several European countries released updates for third quarter GDP data.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The central bank decision from New Zealand was among the main news in Asia.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"score\": 0.8936283220290211, \"rank\": 0.0862374407563451, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\"}]}]}"